==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incapability
<hw>In*ca`pa*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The quality of being incapable; incapacity.</def>
<rj><au>Suckling.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Lack of legal qualifications, or of
legal power; <as>as, <ex>incapability</ex> of holding an
office</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incapable</ent>⟦br⟧
